&gt;&gt; Julie Kline: If anybody
has helped with the weaving

00:16:22.990 --> 00:16:25.980
of stories, it's Georgette Dorn.

00:16:25.980 --> 00:16:28.280
Thank you, Georgette.

00:16:29.510 --> 00:16:36.350
