commemorative poster.

00:46:19.820 --> 00:46:22.960
This special poster
features beautiful artwork

00:46:22.960 --> 00:46:26.800
by Americas Award winner
Rafael Lopez, and we invite you

00:46:26.800 --> 00:46:29.090
to take one with you today.

00:46:29.090 --> 00:46:33.160
At this time, please join us
for a reception and book signing

00:46:33.160 --> 00:46:34.860
with this year's winners.

00:46:34.860 --> 00:46:37.410
You're welcome to purchase
titles just through these doors

00:46:37.410 --> 00:46:41.750
to the back, and Ibi and Duncan
will be in the adjacent room.

00:46:41.750 --> 00:46:43.380
Thank you all so
much for coming,

00:46:43.380 --> 00:46:45.510
